snippet.title: Toti: Rise of the Necromancer Trailer
snippet.description:
Heya everyone, this is the first Trailer for Toti: Rise of the Necromancer!
I hope you liked what you saw, cause we cooked up a lot since then :)

Do you want to try out the game? Give some feedback or just want to shitpost skeleton memes?? Then please join the Discord:
https://discord.gg/zE7SPNDs


If the link is broken, please let me know on Blue Sky 
https://bsky.app/profile/nyco.bsky.social
(or discord: nycoisdreaming)
